snippet.textDisplay: Life goes by and we all have grown up, i have so have they. I sure miss the old days. When i used to stay awake all night just to watch their live streams, vote for them, cry while listening to the sad songs. I remember how much it made me happy when i saw them happy; when they went to the japan for the first time, when they won those big awards, when they were with their loved ones. I remember it all and now everythings different, maybe i dont cry like i used to when listening to outer space but this video right here made me realize that i always carry them in my heart; those happy moments, sadness, being proud, all of them. I am so grateful that they gave me something to hold onto and remember proudly.
